Made in the Mountains with Judith Wyder 🏔️

Trail running gives @judithwyder a feeling of freedom, but it hasn’t been without its hurdles. Listen as Judith discusses the highs, the lows and how running & the outdoors has helped to rebuild her confidence.

“I hope that my story can inspire women, it’s important that all genders can take part in competition.”

Discover more from Judith through the link in bio.
